@startuml Component Model and Specifications
!theme plain

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor LightYellow
  BorderColor Black
}

package "Edge Devices" {
  component "OBU\n(On-Board Unit)" as OBU

  note right of OBU
    **Function:** Generate and sign V2X messages
    **Specifications:**
    • Secure hardware (HSM)
    • Key storage
    • IEEE 802.11p/C-V2X protocol
    • ECDSA signature (secp256k1)
  end note
}

package "Edge Computing Layer" {
  component "RSU/Gateway\n(Road Side Unit)" as RSU

  note right of RSU
    **Function:** Aggregate, pre-validate and route
    **Specifications:**
    • Dual connectivity (V2I and internet)
    • Signature validation module
    • Transaction aggregation buffer
    • Latency < 100ms
  end note
}

package "Consensus Layer" {
  component "Validator Node" as Validator
  component "PBFT Algorithm" as PBFT

  note right of Validator
    **Function:** Participate in consensus and maintain ledger
    **Specifications:**
    • Verified identity (PoA)
    • Blockchain client software
      (e.g.: Hyperledger Besu)
    • Fault tolerance: f < n/3
    • TPS: 1000-5000
  end note

  note right of PBFT
    **Consensus Algorithm:**
    **Stages:**
    1. Request
    2. Pre-prepare (Leader proposes)
    3. Prepare (Partial validation)
    4. Commit (Final confirmation)

    **Properties:**
    • Byzantine fault tolerance
    • Deterministic finality
    • Maximum malicious nodes: (n-1)/3
  end note
}

package "Storage Layer" {
  database "Distributed\nBlockchain/DAG" as Ledger

  note right of Ledger
    **Function:** Immutable storage
    **Specifications:**
    • Replication on all nodes
    • Merkle Tree for integrity
    • SHA-256 hash
    • Block size: ~1MB
    • Block time: 2-5s
  end note
}

package "Auxiliary Services" {
  component "Identity/PKI\nService" as PKI
  component "Monitoring\nService" as Monitor

  note right of PKI
    **Function:** Identity management
    **Specifications:**
    • X.509 certificates
    • CA (Certificate Authority)
    • Renewal every 30 days
    • Certificate Revocation List (CRL)
  end note
}

' Connections
OBU --> RSU : Signed V2X\nmessages
RSU --> Validator : Aggregated\ntransactions
Validator --> PBFT : Executes
Validator --> Ledger : Validated\nblocks

RSU --> PKI : Verifies\ncertificates
Validator --> PKI : Queries\nidentities
Validator --> Monitor : Metrics

@enduml
